EARLY BIRD DINNER THEATER
Proudly serving Tampa Bay for over 25 years.
ABOUT US
The Early Bird Dinner Theater is a family run business serving the greater Tampa Bay area for over 25 years. During that time we have become one of the most popular attractions in Tampa Bay. Our founder, Ed Fletcher, believed in providing first class entertainment and dining for a reasonable price. Our shows are always funny and entertaining performed by professional actors with years of experience. Our food is provided by Banquet Masters, an onsite, chef owned, full service catering company that has also been in business for over 25 years.
We look forward to seeing you soon and providing you with an unique, fun, and exciting entertainment and dining experience that you and your friends will want to repeat over and over again. Call (727) 446-5898 for reservations.
FOOD & BEVERAGE
What's for Dinner?
Join us for our traditional salad bar and delicious full buffet.  Hand sanitizer is on all tables and masks are optional.
If you opt to not partake in the delicious meal,  “show-only” is always an option for $30.
Virginia Baked Ham, Carved Top Round Roast Beef with Au Jus and Horseradish, Salmon Almondine, Seasonal Chicken Entree, and Meatballs in Marinara Sauce or Baked Ziti. Rounding out the menu we have our sides selections which include Seasonal Rice, Mashed Potatoes, and Vegetables. After dinner, enjoy coffee and your choice of dessert as you prepare for the show.
The Early Bird Dinner Theater has a full bar available.  Gatsby’s has a complete selection of premium and top shelf liquor with very reasonably priced bottles of wine.
